{"tid":1419069,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《突發》美國將中國列為匯率操縱國","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:37:56.000Z","uid":13663,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd9d27189e4829244b304a1cd7dd117714225cc","tid":1419069,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:32:26.000Z","msg":"人民幣匯率自2008年來，首度跌穿七算的心理關口後，美國財政部正式將中國列為匯率操縱國。<br />\n<br />\n財政部發表聲明，批評中國在中美貿易戰升溫時，削弱人民幣匯率，財長努欽在總統特朗普的支持下，確認中國為匯率操縱國，努欽將與國際貨幣基金組織商討，消除中國最新行動帶來的不公平競爭優勢。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前在社交網站貼文，指中國讓他們的貨幣貶值到歷史低位，這些叫「操縱匯率」，是嚴重違規。<br />\n<br />\n人民銀行行長易綱說，8月以來很多貨幣兌美元貶值，人民幣匯率亦受一定程度影響，波動是市場驅動及決定，強調中國堅持市場決定的匯率制度，不搞競爭性貶值，不將匯率用於競爭目的，亦不會將匯率作為應對貿易爭端等的工具。"},{"pid":"ad79c7e7866ab3b9811063c9529fd5e4839a9255","tid":1419069,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:32:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472962-20190806.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472962-20190806.htm&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKYpBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=81d9e4db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472962-20190806.htm&h=59149c16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472962-20190806.htm</a>"},{"pid":"74a77b3f707d824635f68bb34c3ba71c3cbae874","tid":1419069,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:33:23.000Z","msg":"要來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea585e215903d2d2e4c488ad1a17eb6ca1c3a7ff","tid":1419069,"uid":262557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150cd977b1f6d22a5f52743ad2b604b584fb7b66","tid":1419069,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img sr